<ion-view title="重置密码" class="stable-bg">

    <ion-content>
        <div style="font-size: 12pt;color: #555;margin-top: 20px;padding:0 5%;">
            <p>{{user.UserName}}，您好。</p>

            <p>您的密码将被重置，重置后的密码会发送到{{user.EmailAddress}}邮箱。</p>

            <p>是否确认重置密码?</p>
        </div>
        <button style="color: #0099ff;margin-top: 20px;width: 90%;min-height: 35px !important;line-height: 35px;margin-left: 5%;"
                class="button" ng-click="resetPassword()">确定
        </button>
    </ion-content>
</ion-view>